#. type: Plain text
#: ../sys-utils/mount.8.adoc:695
msgid ""
"For example, X-mount.auto-fstypes=\"ext4,btrfs\" accepts only ext4 and "
"btrfs, and X-mount.auto-fstypes=\"novfat,xfs\" accepts all filesystems "
"except vfat and xfs."
