msgstr "mailto:werner@suse.de[Werner Fink], mailto:kzak@redhat.com[Karel Zak]"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../term-utils/agetty.8.adoc:340
msgid ""
"The original *agetty* for serial terminals was written by mailto:wietse@wzv."
